        "description": {
            "value": "<p>You're as skilled in combat underwater as on land. You gain the @UUID[Compendium.pf2e.feats-srd.Item.Underwater Marauder] skill feat, and when you roll a success on an Athletics check to Swim, you get a critical success instead. In addition, checks to [[/act escape]] or [[/act force-open]] nets you use are attempted against your class DC instead of the listed DC, and you can keep hold of a target you've grappled with a net with one hand.</p>"
        },
